# Document specifications

## README.md specification
- Keep the document structure clear and use appropriate Markdown tags
- * * Important * *: Ensure that the README includes the following parts:
- Project Introduction
- Installation instructions
- Usage method
- Contribution Guide (if applicable)
- License information

## CHANGELOG.md specification
When requesting an update to CHANGELOG.md, please update in the following format:
```
## v1.0.0
-New feature: Reset device ID
-Fix bug: fix the issue of device ID reset failure
```

## Document update principle
- Keep documents and code updated synchronously
- Use concise and clear language
- Provide sufficient examples and explanations
- Ensure consistent document format
